description:
This is the R code of the data analysis and modelling procedure to quantify the feed intake response of growing pigs to perturbations. The procedure includes four steps: (1) treatment of missing data; (2) estimation of the target trajectory of cumulative feed intake; (3) detection of perturbations based on the differences between observed feed intake and its target and (4) characterization and quantification of animal&#39;s response to perturbations. 

 For detail description of the procedure please see  this article  (DOI:  https://doi.org/10.1017/S1751731119001976  )&nbsp; 

 &nbsp;

